CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, October 23, 1965, pg. 6 reads: "Newlyweds - Mr. and Mrs. Wayne Leonard Carroll were recently married in Sixth Mt. Zion Baptist Church. The bride is the former Rose Ann Simpkins, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Ellis J. Simpkins of Penn Hills -Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wedding party with two men, including groom Wayne Leonard Carroll, second from left, and two women, including bride Rose Ann Simpkins Carroll, second from right, posed in interior of Greene Hearth, another version
